Information Collection
We collect minimal information to help you monitor your servers.
Data Storage
All server credentials are stored locally on your device.
Server credentials are securely stored in iOS Keychain
SSH keys and passwords never leave your device
Monitoring data is only stored temporarily for display
Data Security
We take appropriate security measures to protect your information.
All server communication is end-to-end encrypted
Credentials are stored securely in iOS Keychain
No sensitive data is stored on our servers
Regular security audits and updates
Third-Party Services
We do not share your data with any third-party services. All server monitoring and management functions are performed directly between your device and your servers.
Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page and updating the 'last updated' date.
